<br>
The drop rates are WAY WAY WAY too low.  Lower than any other expansion before.  Yes lower than Kunark (even lower than Kunark before they fixed those drops).  Yes lower than Velious, and yes even lower than Luclin.<br>
<br>
Each succeeding level of parchment is at least an order of magnitude rarer than the previous ones.  You need third tier access to have any real shot at getting a Spectral parchment, and you need to be in a guild capable of killing a third tier boss to be able to get a Shadowy.  That sucks, bad, as there are about two guilds per server that currently can access third tier content.<br>
<br>
Sayleth<br>
